   Jesuh thawngin
   Jesuh thawngin, ka Taltling, Jesuh thawngin,
   Ka hnangam, Jesuh thawngin, Hla ka sa,
   Jesuh thawngin, Jesuh thawngin.

[V2]
 Jesuh cu ka, thazang asi
 Jesuh cu ka, tthawnnak asi
 Jesuh Khrih, thawngin kei ka, dam cang.
 Jesuh cu ka Dornak a si, Jesuh cu ka Himnak asi
 Jesuh khrih Thawngin, kei ka luat cang.</lyrics>
